message.body:
You. And me. Need to do something. I miss you!!!!!!
I've sent this about 4 times. Each time it said my phone didn't send it. I don't know if it did or not.
If it did, I'm sorry that you just got 5 of the same text from me
No no. You're good. I only got it once. But I just put in my schedule for the next six weeks so once the official one comes out, we can figure something out. We do need to go out.
Right?! I've been out with Phuong and sammy separately within the past couple of months and not you! My heart is crying! Mondays and Fridays I'm home by 230 and Thursdays I'm home around 1030.
